Certainly! Below is an example CSV file content listing all U.S. Presidents (as of my last update in 2023) along with their respective details:


Please note that for presidents who served partial terms (like William Henry Harrison and Gerald Ford), the "Years Served" is approximate. Also, Grover Cleveland's two non-consecutive terms are listed separately.

You can copy this content into a text file and save it with a `.csv` extension to work with it in spreadsheet software like Microsoft Excel or Google Sheets.
